<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink55-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">varainta aṇimaik kaṇṇē puṟattoḻukkam oḻuki vāyil vēṇṭivantu taṉ melivu kūṟiya talaimakaṉait tōḻi neruṅkic colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink55">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>karumpi ṉentiraṅ kaḷiṟṟetir piḷiṟṟun</l>
<l>tērvaṇ kōmāṉ ṟēṉū raṉṉaviva</l>
<l>ṇallaṇi nayantunī tuṟattaliṟ</l>
<l>pallō raṟiyap pacantaṉṟu nutalē.</l>
</lg>

<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">



<l>   The girl who is like Tēṉūr, </l> 
<l rend="indent2"> [that city] of a king rich in chariots,</l> 
<l rend="indent2"> where the sugarcane press thunders </l>
  <l> in competition with the elephant bulls – </l> 
<l> Because you abandoned [her],</l> 
<l rend="indent2"> after covetting [her] good beauty/ after longing to get close [to her],   </l> 
<l> [her] forehead has paled </l> 
<l> for all to see. </l> 



</lg>
    </div>
